Author: bad_sharpener
Text: Oh god I know the feeling so much. But for me, I get these huge cravings at night where I'm in my room and I'm thinking about the food that I know are tucked away in the kitchen and that's all I'll be thinking about. I used to be really bad at controlling myself, as I end up giving in to those cravings and eat who knows what, but now I just make sure I brush my teeth early and go straight to bed, whilst my stomach is DYING for a snack.
